Q15.Create a XML file which gives details of movies available in "Movie CD Store" from following categories 

i.Classical 
ii.Horror 
iii.Action Elements in each category are in the following format 
<Category>
<MovieTitle>.............</MovieTitle>
<ActorName>.............</ActorName>
<ReleaseYear>.............</ReleaseYear>
</Category>
Save the file with name "movies.xml". 

Answer:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<movie>
	<Category name="Classical">
	<MovieTitle>Sita Ramam</MovieTitle>
	<ActorName>Salmaan Dulquer</ActorName>
	<ReleaseYear>2022</ReleaseYear>
	</Category>
	
	<Category name="Horror">
	<MovieTitle>Raaz</MovieTitle>
	<ActorName>Emraan Hashmi</ActorName>
	<ReleaseYear>2002</ReleaseYear>
	</Category>
	
	<Category name="Action">
	<MovieTitle>War</MovieTitle>
	<ActorName>Hrithik Roshan</ActorName>
	<ReleaseYear>2019</ReleaseYear>
	</Category>
</movie>
